The unlucky high school cheerleader was helping string a banner to herald the players' arrival on the pitch when disaster struck.
11:24PM BST 09 Oct 2013
Amateur video captured during at the Edna Karr High School in New Orleans shows a cheerleader being unwittingly trampled underfoot by members of the school's American football team.
The girl, who has yet to be identified, is seen suddenly running in front a banner placed on the pitch to herald the arrival of the team, known as the Cougars. But before she has time to react, the players burst through the banner, sending her flying to the ground while the team charge over her prone figure.
